<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-7"><a href="#Efficient_computation_of_Bernoulli_numbers"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Efficient computation of Bernoulli numbers</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-8"><a href="#Different_viewpoints_and_conventions"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Different viewpoints and conventions</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-9"><a href="#Applications_of_the_Bernoulli_numbers"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Applications of the Bernoulli numbers</span></a>
