<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Bernoulli_number&amp;action=edit&amp;section=45" title="Edit section: References">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
