<li><span class="citation web">Gottfried Helms. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://go.helms-net.de/math/binomial/04_3_SummingOfLikePowers.pdf">"summing of like powers in context with Pascal-/Bernoulli-matrix"</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABernoulli+number&amp;rft.au=Gottfried+Helms&amp;rft.aulast=Gottfried+Helms&amp;rft.btitle=summing+of+like+powers+in+context+with+Pascal-%2FBernoulli-matrix&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fgo.helms-net.de%2Fmath%2Fbinomial%2F04_3_SummingOfLikePowers.pdf&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
